{"id":314733,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/09/维权网-浙江丽水政府暴力征地，村民丁友仁被殴/","date":"2013-09-23T03:04:33Z","modified":"2013-09-23T03:04:33Z","title":"维权网 | 浙江丽水政府暴力征地，村民丁友仁被殴打致重伤（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员方芳报道）浙江省丽水市青田县腊口镇政府强征村民土地，对不同意被征收的村民实施殴打。村民丁友仁遭镇政府官员和村委书记指使的人野蛮暴力殴打，致使丁友仁被打掉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>颗门牙，左侧肋骨骨折，双肺挫伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据了解，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年初，青田县腊口镇政府制定了要将腊口建设为“青田县西部重镇</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">”</span><span>的方针，实施“积极拓宽工业发展空间，加大工业园区的开发力度，努力吸引企业落户腊口”的各项的措施，疯狂强征农民的土地，对稍有反抗者实施野蛮暴力手段，威胁逼迫村民同意出让土地。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>据丁友仁的妻子程囡珠陈述：</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">7</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">6</span><span>日，青田县腊口镇政府某些官员和我们村（武埠村）书记涂和平，雇佣本村村民邓小伟对我老公丁友仁实施惨无人道的暴力殴打。邓小伟将丁友仁打倒在地后，手拿石头朝丁友仁劈头盖脸不断猛击。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>丽水市中心医院的诊断证明显示，丁友仁被打掉</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>颗门牙，左侧第</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>肋骨骨折，双肺挫伤。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>丁友仁被打伤后，我们向腊口镇派出所报案并多次要求公安机关立案捉拿打人凶手。但时至今日，打人凶手依然逍遥法外，派出所百般推诿，拒绝立案处理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>我们全家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>口人上有</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>多岁的公公，下有还在读小学的孩子，都靠丁友仁来养活。现在他们将我老公打伤在家不能干活，让我们这个本来就不富裕的家庭更加雪上加霜。现在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">70</span><span>多岁的公公急火攻心，又患上了心脏病，我们却无钱给他医治。我们只是个小老百姓，叫天天不应叫地地不灵，有理也无处说啊！　</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>：丁友仁被打掉门牙的照片</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>图</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>：丁友仁的诊断证明</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-0D3qhKVCNWY/Uj79k1Qi7KI/AAAAAAAAofA/Q6ZseSqoVSs/s1600/1+(2).jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"213\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-0D3qhKVCNWY/Uj79k1Qi7KI/AAAAAAAAofA/Q6ZseSqoVSs/s1600/1+(2).jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TLw0RneK8AY/Uj79lZ9QmcI/AAAAAAAAofI/DJMLXl0_lbo/s1600/2+(2).jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TLw0RneK8AY/Uj79lZ9QmcI/AAAAAAAAofI/DJMLXl0_lbo/s320/2+(2).jpg\" width=\"247\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}